Field Documentation

uint32_t CSL_DssCbaCfg::priHigh

Priority level for high priority mflag transactions. Value of 0x0 indicates highest priority & value of 0x7 indicates lowest priority

uint32_t CSL_DssCbaCfg::priLow

Priority level for normal non-mflag transactions. Value of 0x0 indicates highest priority & value of 0x7 indicates lowest priority
